lyrics:
Bethlehem arsi chu a lo eng,
Thangvan sangah khian in;
Khawchhak mifingte a hruai thleng a,
Nausen Isua hnenah.

Aw Bethlehem arsi eng mawi chu;
Tunah hian kan chungah loeng leh la;
Chutin khawvel Chhandamtu hnen,
Min hruai thleng ngei ang che.

Mifingte chu an lawm em em a,
Arsi eng an hmuh chuan;
An ro hlu berte an la chhuak a,
Lal thar chibai buk nan.

Keini pawhin arsi chu enin,
Kan ro hlu berte nen;
Kan tana Lalber thar lo piang chu,
Chibai i buk ve ang.
